  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK610">
<l>maṭiyiṉmai maṭiyilā maṉṉava ṉeytu </l>
<l>maṭiyaḷantāṉ ṟāaya tellā moruṅku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king who never gives way to idleness will obtain entire possession of (the whole earth) passed over by him who measured (the worlds) with His foot.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
